race.comment: THE SPRINKLER (5) is busting to break through following three strong finishes to open the prep. Peaking now and keeps Toeroek from a favourable draw. Ready. HEADPHONES (6) is ticking along beautifully without winning but this looks her best chance yet. Loves this trip and should blend into the race nicely from her draw. Watch for her charging at the business end. CIELAO (7) has been terrific this prep and is sure to give herself every chance again in front, though she's expected to have company. TAPINFORPAR (2) returned in career-best touch at Gawler when sticking her neck out at long odds. Has been kept fresh as she rises to a trip she loves. Drawn well and has to be taken seriously. ZARKANA (11) was a barnstorming winner fresh. Hasn't quite been able to replicate but has been finishing strongly. Will drift back again and be saved for the final shot at them.
